What it does
============

 - if, while, for, break, continue, return
 - functions
 - single dimension arrays
 - c style comments
 - c++ style comments
 - contstant folding
 - dead code removal
 - instruction level concurrency

What it doesn't
===============

 - no libc
 - no float or double
 - no recursion
 - no pointers
 - no case

Extensions
==========

 - report statement
 - assert statement
 - synthesisable wait_clocks statement
